   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-accepting-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-accepting-h" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yeah. A warrior named Gerard was guarding it.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>
