If we find that ancient temple, we can find out more about the Brotherhood of Steel as well as Barnac's treasures...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-accepting-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-accepting-i" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>But he had turned into a Death Knight.</html>]]></talk_answer>
